              "         border-bottom: 1px solid var(--colab-border-color);\"><b>google.colab.files.download</b><br/>def download(filename)</pre><pre class=\"function-repr-contents function-repr-contents-collapsed\" style=\"\"><a class=\"filepath\" style=\"display:none\" href=\"#\">/usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages/google/colab/files.py</a>Downloads the file to the user&#x27;s local disk via a browser download action.\n",
              "\n",
